<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Broon is easy. sure he cons 23... but that dont mean shiest<BR>
 in his case. any lvl 20 mage worth his stuff could solo him<BR>
. warriors... no. sorry but your soloing abilities are next <BR>
to nill ;)alright at 20.. go to HK get on main room list..youll <BR>
porbably be around 7 on an average day.. 17 on a busy day<BR>
 and 3 on your lucky day. then get an SoW from yer local<BR>
 druid and or shaman and head out to EK! He spawns out by a<BR>
 lone tree towards the end of the ramp(hint: Levitate is <BR>
fun and safe here :) it could save your life) after he <BR>
spawns(his spawning time is 5min.. not bad for a lvl 23 mob ;) )<BR>
 he'll head out for the river..if he does this youd better <BR>
have yer running shoes on because once he dies...big brother<BR>
droon spawns right at the river where broon stops to bathe<BR>
Droon=35 PO'ed clopse. there obviously a close family because<BR>
Droon no like you smash his brother. thats why you wanna kill<BR>
Broon close to his spawning point. Once droon spawns hell eventually<BR>
kill himself (after of course a bunch of idiots agro him and <BR>
train him to the bridge of course but you can sit back and<BR>
laugh ;) ) So then all you gotta do is camp at the edge of <BR>
ramp..nuke and enjoy :) his loots noit that great but its bettee<BR>
than sitting waiting for main room list ;)</font></td></tr></table>
