<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just some additional info.  Once you have killed Broon, Droon will spawn.  He is level 30 not 35.  Once he is killed, Proon will occasionally spawn, who I believe is level 37.  Broon Spawns at the ramp to HHP then runs to the bridge.  Broon drops rusty weapons, and occasionally 1-2 plat, and cyclops toes.<BR>
